{"tid":2452484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普卸任後曝光率大減　CNN收視暴跌34%","createTime":"2021-03-19T00:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T05:07:11.000Z","uid":28765,"like":307,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"fca837db37e2bcbdcebbc27a9f88a004f89fdc95","tid":2452484,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:53:49.000Z","msg":"過去四年積極批評時任美國總統川普的有線電視新聞網（CNN），在川普卸任後，收視率暴跌34%，每日平均觀眾由過去的250萬人，大跌至110萬人；晚上黃金時段的主要年齡層觀眾流失率更高達47%，分析指與川普曝光率減少有關。<br />\n<br />\n福斯新聞報導，去年大選後第二日（11月4日）到今年拜登宣誓就職總統當日（1月20日），CNN平均每日有170萬名收看觀眾，晚上8時至11時的黃金時段，平均觀眾多達250萬人。而去年12月28日至今年1月20日，即川普支持者闖入國會期間發生的相關新聞，CNN平均每日收看人數更增加至220萬人，黃金時段觀眾增至310萬人。<br />\n<br />\n...."},{"pid":"2e14e28e210ea22c1bc4d4e57b1acecd1a3d03e4","tid":2452484,"uid":28765,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:54:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210319/ZHFENWD2UNEFRGB43G63AUDGOM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FZHFENWD2UNEFRGB43G63AUDGOM%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBStHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=8e42910e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FZHFENWD2UNEFRGB43G63AUDGOM%2F&h=150b5b0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210319/ZHFENWD2UNEFRGB43G63AUDGOM/</a>"},{"pid":"f23de04198443ffc0d256428b55984f88628a5f9","tid":2452484,"uid":100772,"like":337,"dislike":2,"score":335,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:55:04.000Z","msg":"轉屌拜登咪得  邊個做咪屌邊個"},{"pid":"9d2d90ecc66905ad2e47a6df7cc95ff9415c6121","tid":2452484,"uid":51753,"like":165,"dislike":1,"score":164,"quote":{"pid":"f23de04198443ffc0d256428b55984f88628a5f9","tid":2452484,"uid":100772,"like":337,"dislike":2,"score":335,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:55:04.000Z","msg":"轉屌拜登咪得  邊個做咪屌邊個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:19:07.000Z","msg":"正常一定係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 